ConfigMaps & Secrets:


What is ConfigMap:

A specifc env file and other file  how to acess that file so by the config map you access the file and also read the file

The config map is solving the problem to  store the information  that can be used as later,

Secrets:
If you put any  type of data so it will encrypt the data , you also  add cutsom encryption

What is diifence between COnfigmap and Secrets:

Both are store the data but configmap is used for non sensitive information and secretus is used for store sensitive information

